header(class="sticky top-0 z-20 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950/95")
    div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-5 py-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
        div
            div(class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-globe")
                span Domains
            h1(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 도메인 관리
        div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
            button(type="button", (click)="openDdnsModal()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                span DDNS 서버 추가

main(class="space-y-5 px-5 py-5")
    div(*ngIf="loading()", class="h-32 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 정보를 불러오는 중입니다.
    div(*ngIf="error()", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{error()}}

    div(*ngIf="!loading() && !error()", class="space-y-5")
        section(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
            div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between")
                div
                    div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                        h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") DDNS 관리 서버
                        span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="ddnsDispatcherBadgeClass()") {{ddnsDispatcherLabel()}}
                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서비스 도메인은 등록된 DDNS wildcard suffix 하위 주소로만 생성됩니다.
                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                    span(class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300") 서버 {{ddnsSummary().endpoint_count || ddnsEndpoints().length}}개
                    span(class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300") 등록 {{ddnsSummary().registration_count || ddnsRegistrations().length}}개
                    button(*ngIf="ddnsDispatcher()?.registered !== true", type="button", (click)="ensureDdnsDispatcher()", [disabled]="ddnsDispatcherBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-amber-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-amber-700 hover:bg-amber-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:text-amber-300 dark:hover:bg-amber-950/30")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-plug-circle-plus")
                        span {{ddnsDispatcherBusy() ? '등록 중...' : 'Dispatcher 등록'}}
                    button(type="button", (click)="openDdnsModal()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                        span 추가
            div(*ngIf="ddnsWarning()", class="border-b border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-amber-800 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:bg-amber-950/30 dark:text-amber-200") {{ddnsWarning()}}
            div(*ngIf="!ddnsWarning() && ddnsEndpoints().length === 0", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 등록된 DDNS 관리 서버가 없습니다.
            div(*ngIf="ddnsEndpoints().length > 0", class="overflow-x-auto")
                table(class="w-full min-w-[1100px] table-fixed divide-y divide-zinc-100 text-sm dark:divide-zinc-800")
                    thead(class="bg-zinc-50 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400")
                        tr
                            th(class="w-32 px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 서버명
                            th(class="w-24 whitespace-nowrap px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 상태
                            th(class="w-36 px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") Wildcard suffix
                            th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") DDNS 서버 API
                            th(class="w-36 whitespace-nowrap px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") Dispatcher 요청
                            th(class="w-28 whitespace-nowrap px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") IP
                            th(class="w-28 px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") Host
                            th(class="w-24 px-4 py-2 text-center font-semibold") 등록
                            th(class="w-36 px-4 py-2 text-right font-semibold") 작업
                    tbody(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                        tr(*ngFor="let endpoint of pagedDdnsEndpoints()", class="align-top")
                            td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{endpoint.name || endpoint.domain_suffix}}
                            td(class="whitespace-nowrap px-4 py-3")
                                span(class="inline-flex whitespace-nowrap rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(endpoint.status)") {{ddnsStatusLabel(endpoint)}}
                            td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                span(class="inline-flex max-w-full rounded-md border border-violet-200 bg-violet-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-violet-700 dark:border-violet-900/70 dark:bg-violet-950/40 dark:text-violet-300")
                                    span(class="truncate") *.{{endpoint.domain_suffix}}
                            td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                p(class="break-all font-mono text-xs text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") {{endpoint.api_url || endpoint.api_base_url}}
                            td(class="whitespace-nowrap px-4 py-3")
                                p(class="truncate whitespace-nowrap text-xs font-medium text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200", [title]="formatDate(endpoint.dispatcher?.last_sent_at)") {{formatDate(endpoint.dispatcher?.last_sent_at)}}
                            td(class="whitespace-nowrap px-4 py-3")
                                p(class="truncate whitespace-nowrap font-mono text-xs text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200", [title]="endpoint.dispatcher?.last_sent_ip || '-'") {{endpoint.dispatcher?.last_sent_ip || '-'}}
                            td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                p(class="truncate text-xs font-medium text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") {{endpoint.dispatcher?.last_hostname || '-'}}
                                p(class="mt-1 text-[11px] text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500") agent 레코드 {{endpoint.dispatcher?.record_count || 0}}개
                            td(class="whitespace-nowrap px-4 py-3 text-center")
                                div(class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1")
                                    span(class="inline-flex min-w-[4rem] justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-200") {{endpointRegistrationCount(endpoint)}}개
                            td(class="whitespace-nowrap px-4 py-3")
                                div(class="flex flex-nowrap items-center justify-end gap-1 whitespace-nowrap")
                                    button(type="button", (click)="forceUpdateDdnsEndpoint(endpoint)", [disabled]="ddnsUpdateEndpointId() === endpoint.id", title="DDNS API 호출", aria-label="DDNS API 호출", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-sky-300 text-xs font-semibold text-sky-700 hover:bg-sky-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-60 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:text-sky-300 dark:hover:bg-sky-950/30")
                                        i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="ddnsUpdateEndpointId() === endpoint.id ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-arrows-rotate'")
                                    button(type="button", (click)="openDdnsModal(endpoint)", title="DDNS 서버 수정", aria-label="DDNS 서버 수정", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-pen")
                                    button(type="button", (click)="deleteDdnsEndpoint(endpoint)", title="DDNS 서버 삭제", aria-label="DDNS 서버 삭제", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-rose-300 text-xs font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-trash")
            div(*ngIf="ddnsEndpointPagination().total > 0", class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-t border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
                p(class="text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 페이지당 20개
                wiz-portal-season-pagination([current]="ddnsEndpointPagination().current", [start]="ddnsEndpointPagination().start", [end]="ddnsEndpointPagination().end", [maxlength]="10", (pageMove)="moveDdnsEndpointPage($event)")

        section(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
            div(class="flex flex-col gap-2 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
                div
                    h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 등록된 DDNS 레코드
                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서비스 배포가 DDNS API로 등록한 hostname, 연결 서비스, Docker Infra 연결 대상입니다.
                span(class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-300") {{ddnsRegistrations().length}}개
            div(*ngIf="ddnsRegistrations().length === 0", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 등록된 DDNS 레코드가 없습니다.
            div(*ngIf="ddnsRegistrations().length > 0", class="overflow-x-auto")
                table(class="w-full min-w-[1040px] table-fixed divide-y divide-zinc-100 text-sm dark:divide-zinc-800")
                    thead(class="bg-zinc-50 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400")
                        tr
                            th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") Hostname
                            th(class="w-48 px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 연결 서비스
                            th(class="w-56 px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 연결 대상
                            th(class="w-36 px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") DDNS 서버
                            th(class="w-24 px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 상태
                            th(class="w-36 px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 마지막 갱신
                    tbody(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                        tr(*ngFor="let item of pagedDdnsRegistrations()", class="align-top")
                            td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                a([href]="registrationHostnameHref(item)", target="_blank", rel="noopener noreferrer", class="inline-flex max-w-full items-center font-semibold text-zinc-950 hover:underline dark:text-zinc-50")
                                    span(class="min-w-0 break-all") {{item.domain}}
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square ml-2 mr-2 flex-none text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{item.remote_record_id || '-'}}
                            td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                                    div(class="min-w-0")
                                        p(class="truncate text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100") {{registrationServiceLabel(item)}}
                                        p(class="mt-1 truncate text-[11px] text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500") {{registrationServiceSubtitle(item)}}
                                    a(*ngIf="hasLinkedService(item)", [routerLink]="serviceDetailLink(item)", title="서비스 상세", [attr.aria-label]="'서비스 상세로 이동'", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-md text-zinc-500 hover:bg-zinc-100 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:hover:text-zinc-100")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square")
                            td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                                    div(class="min-w-0")
                                        p(class="break-words text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") {{registrationTargetTitle(item)}}
                                        p(*ngIf="registrationTargetSubtitle(item)", class="mt-1 break-words text-[11px] text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{registrationTargetSubtitle(item)}}
                                    a(*ngIf="hasTargetDetail(item)", [routerLink]="targetDetailLink(item)", title="서버 상세", [attr.aria-label]="'서버 상세로 이동'", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-md text-zinc-500 hover:bg-zinc-100 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:hover:text-zinc-100")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-server")
                            td(class="px-4 py-3 text-xs text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300") {{registrationEndpointLabel(item)}}
                            td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(item.status)") {{registrationStatusLabel(item)}}
                            td(class="px-4 py-3 text-xs text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300") {{formatDate(item.last_sync_at)}}
            div(*ngIf="ddnsRegistrationPagination().total > 0", class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-t border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
                p(class="text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 페이지당 20개
                wiz-portal-season-pagination([current]="ddnsRegistrationPagination().current", [start]="ddnsRegistrationPagination().start", [end]="ddnsRegistrationPagination().end", [maxlength]="10", (pageMove)="moveDdnsRegistrationPage($event)")

div(*ngIf="ddnsModalOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/50 px-4 py-6")
    div(class="w-full max-w-2xl rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-2xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            div
                h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{ddnsForm.id ? 'DDNS 서버 수정' : 'DDNS 서버 추가'}}
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") DDNS 관리 시스템에서 발급받은 wildcard 권한과 API Key를 등록합니다.
            button(type="button", (click)="closeDdnsModal()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 p-5 md:grid-cols-2")
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 이름
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="ddnsForm.name", placeholder="Season DDNS", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Wildcard suffix
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="ddnsForm.domain_suffix", placeholder="sub.season.co.kr", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 예: 부여받은 권한이 *.sub.season.co.kr이면 sub.season.co.kr만 입력하세요.
            label(class="block md:col-span-2")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") DDNS 서버 API
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="ddnsForm.api_url", placeholder="http://ddns.nanoha.kr/api/ddns/update", autocomplete="new-password", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Docker Infra가 DNS 레코드 등록/갱신을 요청할 전체 API URL입니다.
            label(class="block md:col-span-2")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") API Token
                div(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                    input([type]="ddnsForm.token_visible ? 'text' : 'password'", [(ngModel)]="ddnsForm.token_value", [placeholder]="ddnsForm.id ? '비워두면 기존 token을 유지합니다' : '발급받은 API Token을 입력하세요'", autocomplete="new-password", class="h-10 min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                    button(type="button", (click)="ddnsForm.token_visible = !ddnsForm.token_visible", class="inline-flex h-10 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                        i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="ddnsForm.token_visible ? 'fa-eye-slash' : 'fa-eye'")
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 해당 wildcard suffix에 대해 DDNS 관리 시스템에서 발급한 API Key입니다.
            div(class="md:col-span-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-2 dark:border-zinc-800")
                label(class="flex items-start gap-3")
                    input(type="checkbox", [(ngModel)]="ddnsForm.tls_verify", class="mt-1")
                    span
                        span(class="block text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") HTTPS 인증서 검증
                        span(class="mt-1 block text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 켜두면 DDNS 서버 API의 HTTPS 인증서를 검증합니다. 자체 서명/사설 인증서를 쓰는 서버에서만 끄세요.
        div(class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 border-t border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            button(type="button", (click)="closeDdnsModal()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                span 취소
            button(type="button", (click)="saveDdnsEndpoint()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk")
                span 저장
